FBIS3-11997 "drlat060_o_94006" FBIS-LAT-94-060 Document Type:Daily Report 26 Mar 1994 Colombia Pepes Leader Denies `Threats' to Escobar's Widow PA2803152894 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 1 in Spanish 1800 GMT 26 Mar 94 PA2803152894 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 1 Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN ["Last-minute report" from the "NTC News" newscast] [Text] Maria Victoria Henao, Pablo Escobar's widow, has just received a letter signed by Fidel Castano, who is said to be the leader of the Pepes [Persecuted by Pablo Escobar]. Castano says he is not the author of the threats received by the Escobar family in the past days.
